description.en:
Cry Coin is a decentralised Solana-chain meme token. Its purpose is to celebrate the sad cat meme, wherein very sad cat eyes are photoshopped on cat pictures.

We are building a fun community centered around this meme and meme token. Our greater plans involve establishing a meme-exchange where ephemeral memes can be speculated upon financially, built on top of the Solana chain.
